{{Infobox organization | nom =Center for European Studies at Sciences Po | logo = | taille logo = 230 | création = [[2005]] | siège = [[Paris]] | pays =[[France]] | disciplines = | rattachement =[[Fondation nationale des sciences politiques]] | directeur =[[Renaud Dehousse]] | chercheurs statutaires = | chercheurs associés = | doctorants = | site = }}
The '''Center for European Studies at Sciences Po''' is one of the nine research centres at the [[Institut d'études politiques de Paris|IEP de Paris]]. It is founded in 2005, by [[Renaud Dehousse]], who is its director.
